Music Downloader & Player

  


---

Overview

This project allows you to download and play music for free by fetching songs directly from YouTube.
It also uses Google Gemini AI to create personalized playlists based on your music preferences.


---

Features

Download and play music from YouTube for free.

AI-powered playlist creation (using Gemini AI).

Fast and reliable downloads via yt-dlp.

Lightweight, responsive frontend.

Easy setup and usage.



---

Setup Instructions

1. Install FFmpeg

Download FFmpeg and install it.

Add FFmpeg to your global system environment path.


2. Install Python Libraries

Make sure you have Python 3.9+ installed.

Install required packages:

pip install -r requirements.txt


3. Configure Gemini API Key

Create a .env file in the root directory.

Add your Gemini API key like this:

GEMINI_API_KEY=your_api_key_here


4. Install Frontend Packages

If the project has a frontend directory, navigate to it and run:

npm install



